      <h3>Learn More</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="http://jquery.com">jQuery</a> The official site contains the API documentation and downloads.</li>
        <li><a href="http://javascriptweekly.com/">Javascript Weekly</a> A concise, onceâ€“weekly free roundup of JavaScript news and articles. Curated by Peter Cooper.</li>
